# locality

**Instance Property**

The city of the place.

## Declaration

```swift
locality?: string;
```

## Discussion

For example, the [doc://com.apple.mapkitjs/documentation/MapKitJS/SearchAutocompleteResult/locality] for Golden Gate Park is `"San Francisco"`.
